#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:417
msgid ""
"Extracts the portions of features from the input layer that overlap features"
" in the overlay layer."
msgstr "入力レイヤの地物のうち、オーバーレイレイヤの地物と重なる部分を抽出します。"

